                The ultimate gamer setup. Includes the exclusive <strong>mausGG6 m5-3.5 Pro</strong> with extra RAM and military-grade components.
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap: 4rem; align-items:center; margin-bottom:3rem;">
                <div style="text-align:left;">
                    <div style="color:#818cf8; font-family:var(--font-mono);">INCLUDES:</div>
                    <ul style="list-style:none; text-align:left; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:bold;">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#4ade80"></i> mausGG6 m5-3.5 PRO</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#4ade80"></i> RGB Mousepad</li>
